// The values are in RBG format. The first argument is 
// an 8 bit integer that represents red. The second argument
// is an 8-bit integer (0-255) that representas Green and the third
// argument is an 8bit integer (0-255) that represents blue. Note
// that the background must be coded before you code
// any other objects or else the background will cover
// any object that is coded prior to "background".

